Two HPGe detectors were used at LANL
1. ORTEC GEM p-type coaxial HPGe detector model
GEM20P-PLUS to measure short and intermediate-lived
species directly at the IPF site
2. ORTEC IDM-200-VTM with a single volume crystal
of 85 mm diameter and 30 mm length and built-in
spectroscopy electronics.
Gamma detectors at BNL included
1. Two EURISYS MESURES 2 Fold Segmented Clover
detectors
2. Two GEM25P4-70 ORTEC GEM coaxial p-type HPGe
detectors
3. ORTEC GAMMA-X n-type coaxial HPGe detector
model GMX-13180
Stack targets were disassembled after
irradiation and periodically counted during 10 min and
20 min counting periods, later the 40 available
targets were periodically counted at positions 15 to
60 cm from the detector faces.
